	layout_mode = 2
	theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 18
	text = "
CONTROLS:
- WASD: Move
- MOUSE: Aim & Shoot
- SHIFT (Hold): Sprint
- Q: Heal (when available)

SYSTEMS:
- RARITY: Gray (Common) < Blue (Rare) < Gold (Epic)
- SUPPLY ZONES: Look for golden pillars in sky. High risk, high reward.
- STEALTH: Bushes reduce visibility. Shooting reveals you.
- ZONE: Stay inside the blue ring to avoid damage.
"
